parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Uncommanded brake application can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: The brakes engage without pressing the brake pedal
the vehicle comes to a complete stop
the vehicle pulls to one side
and the brakes may slip or shimmy.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake pedal issues can cause loss of braking power, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal sticks to the floor
the brake pedal does not return to its normal position
and the brake pedal has a delayed return to its normal position.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Yaw rate sensor failure can cause uncommanded brake application, loss of control, and accidents.
symptoms: the brakes engage without pressing the brake pedal
and the vehicle pulls to one side.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake hydraulic system failure can cause loss of braking power, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: the brake pedal feels soft or spongy
and the brake pedal does not return to its normal position.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Stop light switch failure can cause cruise control malfunction, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The cruise control fails to disengage
and the BAS/ESP light comes on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake noise and vibration can cause driver distraction, loss of control, and accidents.
symptoms: The brakes make a loud noise or squealing sound
and the vehicle vibrates when braking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the AAM can cause multiple electrical components to malfunction, including door locks, windows, mirrors, and other systems, leading to inconvenience, safety risks, and potential accidents.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Power Steering Fluid Leaks and Clamp Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the loss of power steering, making it difficult to steer the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: steering wheel locked or difficult to turn.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering pump can cause the loss of power steering, making it difficult to steer the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: steering wheel locked or difficult to turn.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering column and rack/pinion can cause the loss of power steering, making it difficult to steer the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: steering wheel locked or difficult to turn.
